title: Wicked Swing [FLAC+MP3](Big Papi) VA Artie Duke Glenn Benny Etc
description:
Source: CD



By COMPUTERJAZZMAN

You can have all of your modern day neuvo swing music stuff, (Brian Setzer, Big Bad Voodoo Daddy, etc), I like the real, original stuff. And this CD has some of the biggest names playing some great swing stuff that you don't normally hear. Instead of "Swing, Swing, Swing", "A String of Pearls", "In The Mood" and "Begin The Beguine", there'a a lot of other stuff just as great but lesser known.
